{"tid":714242,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯站出來了！帶頭開誓師大會 力除阿根廷內亂","createTime":"2018-06-23T14:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T16:31:28.000Z","uid":20634,"like":77,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"e51fdada4e158547d49ca9f23ea4886a8d1932b9","tid":714242,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/06/23/6/69a53c568bff3279f092f2e78665bd09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F6%2F69a53c568bff3279f092f2e78665bd09.jpg&h=fd1bef34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷召開誓師大會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　根據阿根廷TyC的消息，在昨天阿根廷隊內進行了一次會談，包括美斯，桑保利，馬斯查蘭奴以及足協主席塔皮亞等人紛紛發言。<br />\n<br />\n　　6月22日的這個週五對於阿根廷國家隊來說不是普通的一天，在吃過晚餐並且觀看了尼日利亞和冰島的勝利之後，阿根廷隊內進行了一次嚴肅緊張的對話。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n　　根據TyC消息，在這次會議上，隊長美斯和馬斯查蘭奴首先進行了發言，隨後教練桑保利和足協主席塔皮亞也紛紛發言。<br />\n<br />\n　　這次會議的目的就是為了削除隊內的分歧，並且為下週二的關鍵比賽凝心聚力。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前在與克羅地亞賽後，阿古路曾經對桑保利「戰術沒有成功」的言論回應稱「他愛說啥說啥」。被認為是球隊內部出現了分歧。"},{"pid":"ace5ab4abb42bf09f85a9ca95f1f03b805b4b44c","tid":714242,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efde1c1b100089be389985a0c3b94220046adce1","tid":714242,"uid":21970,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"下場阿古獸仲有得出=小花炒領隊魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b9f83bc4c7ce0576e4ccf078202d21afb1091","tid":714242,"uid":66839,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"重注阿根廷了"},{"pid":"7d9218eb4350533bc29af6f615419f3023fbe7e5","tid":714242,"uid":20634,"like":44,"dislike":7,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隊長氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"